# 62 possession - alienable gyaa form 1p
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {poss}
Mary dalang gyaa ts’agts’aggee qinggan
Mary dalang gyaa ts’agts’ag-gee qing-gan
Mary 2p POSS wagon-DF see-PST
`Mary saw your wagon.'

# 63 possession - alienable gyaa form non-1p
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {poss}
